Content:
@Stone Cold 

Here's a great walkthrough @Mike B just shared with me 🙂

https://youtu.be/c8qNYyeAQBs?feature=shared

@dicoroberto1959  Hey there! Thanks for reaching out about this!

When you switch, you’ll be able to either upgrade at the end of your current subscription or upgrade right away with proration (see the image for reference). If you choose to upgrade immediately, once selecting **continue** a pop-up will appear showing the exact cost difference so you can clearly see how much the upgrade will be.

If you have any questions, please let me know!
